HEADWORD: Sarcel
<hw>Sar"cel</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OF.
<ets>cercel</ets>, F. <ets>cerceau</ets>, L. <ets>circellus</ets>, dim.
of <ets>circulus</ets>. See <er>Circle</er>.]</ety> <def>One of the
